summary: This is an email forwarding a voice message from a wireless caller to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) on July 11, 2019. The message appears to be related to the Epstein case, as indicated by the file reference EFTA00155548.

events.title: Voice Message Forwarded to US Attorney's Office
events.description: A voice message from a wireless caller was forwarded via email to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York.

keyFacts: A voice message from a wireless caller was forwarded to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York on July 11, 2019.
The document is an internal email with an attached audio file (20190711_122806.wav).
The file reference EFTA00155548 suggests this is part of the Epstein case documentation.
The message originated from a Department of Justice VoIP system (postmaster@voip.usa.doj.gov).
No specific individuals are named in the provided text, only institutional email addresses.
